15#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_UNSPEC_103_C
16#define RDATA_GENERIC_UNSPEC_103_C
17
18#define RRTYPE_UNSPEC_ATTRIBUTES (0)
19
20static inline isc_result_t
21fromtext_unspec(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
22
23 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_unspec);
24
25 UNUSED(type);
26 UNUSED(rdclass);
27 UNUSED(origin);
28 UNUSED(options);
29 UNUSED(callbacks);
30
31 return (atob_tobuffer(lexer, target));
32}
33
34static inline isc_result_t
35totext_unspec(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
36
37 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_unspec);
38
39 UNUSED(tctx);
40
41 return (btoa_totext(rdata->data, rdata->length, target));
42}
43
44static inline isc_result_t
45fromwire_unspec(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
46 isc_region_t sr;
47
48 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_unspec);
49
50 UNUSED(type);
51 UNUSED(rdclass);
52 UNUSED(dctx);
53 UNUSED(options);
54
55 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
56 isc_buffer_forward(source, sr.length);
57 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
58}
59
60static inline isc_result_t
61towire_unspec(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
62
63 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_unspec);
64
65 UNUSED(cctx);
66
67 return (mem_tobuffer(target, rdata->data, rdata->length));
68}
69
70static inline int
71compare_unspec(ARGS_COMPARE) {
72 isc_region_t r1;
73 isc_region_t r2;
74
75 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
76 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
77 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_unspec);
78
79 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
80 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
81 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
82}
83
84static inline isc_result_t
85fromstruct_unspec(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
86 dns_rdata_unspec_t *unspec = source;
87
88 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_unspec);
89 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
90 REQUIRE(unspec->common.rdtype == type);
91 REQUIRE(unspec->common.rdclass == rdclass);
92 REQUIRE(unspec->data != NULL || unspec->datalen == 0);
93
94 UNUSED(type);
95 UNUSED(rdclass);
96
97 return (mem_tobuffer(target, unspec->data, unspec->datalen));
98}
99
100static inline isc_result_t
101tostruct_unspec(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
102 dns_rdata_unspec_t *unspec = target;
103 isc_region_t r;
104
105 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_unspec);
106 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
107
108 unspec->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
109 unspec->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
110 ISC_LINK_INIT(&unspec->common, link);
111
112 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
113 unspec->datalen = r.length;
114 unspec->data = mem_maybedup(mctx, r.base, r.length);
115 if (unspec->data == NULL)
116 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
117
118 unspec->mctx = mctx;
119 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
120}
121
122static inline void
123freestruct_unspec(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
124 dns_rdata_unspec_t *unspec = source;
125
126 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
127 REQUIRE(unspec->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_unspec);
128
129 if (unspec->mctx == NULL)
130 return;
131
132 if (unspec->data != NULL)
133 isc_mem_free(unspec->mctx, unspec->data);
134 unspec->mctx = NULL;
135}
136
137static inline isc_result_t
138additionaldata_unspec(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
139 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_unspec);
140
141 UNUSED(rdata);
142 UNUSED(add);
143 UNUSED(arg);
144
145 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
146}
147
148static inline isc_result_t
149digest_unspec(ARGS_DIGEST) {
150 isc_region_t r;
151
152 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_unspec);
153
154 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
155
156 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
157}
158
159static inline bool
160checkowner_unspec(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
161
162 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_unspec);
163
164 UNUSED(name);
165 UNUSED(type);
166 UNUSED(rdclass);
167 UNUSED(wildcard);
168
169 return (true);
170}
171
172static inline bool
173checknames_unspec(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
174
175 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_unspec);
176
177 UNUSED(rdata);
178 UNUSED(owner);
179 UNUSED(bad);
180
181 return (true);
182}
183
184static inline int
185casecompare_unspec(ARGS_COMPARE) {
186 return (compare_unspec(rdata1, rdata2));
187}
